x = np.array([0, 0, 1])
idx_entities = np.array([0, 1, 2, 3])
filter_triples = np.array(([1, 0, 1], [2, 0, 1]))
x_n_actual = generate_corruptions_for_eval(x, idx_entities=idx_entities,
    filter=filter_triples, side='o')
x_n_expected = np.array([[0, 0, 0], [0, 0, 2], [0, 0, 3]])
np.testing.assert_array_equal(np.sort(x_n_actual, axis=0), np.sort(
    x_n_expected, axis=0))
pytest.mark.skip(reason=
    'Needs to change to account for prime-product evaluation strategy')
